name: Super Project Analyzer File
summary: Learn about .SUD files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: SUD files track file usage within a project. The program determines which files are necessary and which are not. Project elements are then labeled as "Included," "Shared," "Used," or "Dead."

description: Project saved by Super Project Analyzer, a program that analyzes software development projects; contains information about files, procedures, constants, variables, data types and enums.
